# mhyprot3.sys


{{< tip "warning" >}}
We were not able to verify the hash of this driver successfully, it has not been confirmed.
{{< /tip >}}


### Description

mhyprot3.sys is a driver associated with the anticheat software used by the gaming company miHoYo.
- **UUID**: 2aa003cd-5f36-46a6-ae3d-f5afc2c8baa3
- **Created**: 2023-01-09
- **Author**: Michael Haag
- **Acknowledgement**:  | [](https://twitter.com/)

```
sc.exe create mhyprot3.sys binPath=C:\windows\temp\mhyprot3.sys type=kernel &amp;&amp; sc.exe start mhyprot3.sys
```
